global.conf
===========

It has a global and a restraint sections. Any section that will help all projects 
should be created in global.conf


{project}.conf
==============

This is project specific configuration file.
* global section here is common to your project. For e.g., some path
* each section matches exactly the JOB_NAME variable from jenkins runtest job
* job_name is the restraint xml file name which is expected to be available in 
  ipa-tests/restraints as per global section
* type is to identify if the tests can be executed in a single node or multi.
  Accepted values: single or multi
* style is to identify if the jenkins project is a free style project or a
  matrix one. Accepted values: free or matrix or whichever JJB supports.
